        <a name="intro">
        <h3>About Project Wonderland Modules</h3></a>
        
        <a name="goals">
        <h4>Vision and Goals</h4></a>
        
        <p>
            Project Wonderland Modules provide a way to extend the Project Wonderland
            core with new run-time functionality. We're adopting a modular approach 
            so that the community can create extensions to Wonderland that plug in
            using a documented module API. This API is currently being designed.
        </p>
        
        <p>
            We'll release several Wonderland applications in this project using a
            preliminary version of the module system.
        </p>
        
